data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This recently updated ranch,  offers a harmonious blend of modern elegance and comfortable living.  With 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a very specious laundry room that could be used for a office space or converted into another bedroom.  Kitchen offers new appliances, and abundant cabinet space for all your culinary endeavors. Open-concept living and dining area, bathed in natural light, create a perfect space for entertaining or relaxing. Bathrooms have contemporary finishes and fixtures, including porcelain tiles.  This home offers a blend of tranquility and easy access to parks, schools Fair Garden Elementary school directly in front of the house, and shopping. Quick access to major highways and public transportation makes commuting a breeze.  Dont miss out!!
